beer.beer_description: Beerfarm Pineapple is a light, summery, smashable berlinner weisse style beer fermented with generous amounts of fresh pineapple. The beer is pungent with tropical & lemony fruit characters, has a lovely clean refreshing acidity and finishes with a big punch of pineapple on the palate.. Also in cans!
